name: HaircutScheduler
0:
”Alexa, open haircut scheduler”
”Alexa, schedule a haircut with haircut scheduler”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: haircut scheduler
des:
With Haircut Scheduler you can stay in fashion easily, just say to the Skill when do you want a haircut and it will schedule it for you!

The skill will ask the time and your name, so it will be able to identify you after. But we don't collect any geolocation or any other private data, we need just a simple name.
